welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Superior! Get ready to experience the charm of our beautiful city known for its stunning scenery and friendly locals. We invite you to explore and enjoy all that Superior has to offer."

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Richard I Bong Airport is the primary hub for all commercial flights.

terminals.name: General Aviation Terminal
terminals.description: The general aviation terminal at Richard I Bong Airport serves private and charter flights.

wifi.note: Complimentary WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Duluth International Airport serves both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Cargo Terminal
terminals.description: The cargo terminal at Duluth International Airport handles all cargo and freight operations.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.
